The '''bo'tous spore''' was a biological weapon developed by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. It was housed in the lungs of a host, who could then exhale the spores in the presence of an intended target. Upon contact with open air, the spores would become [[bo'tous]]. A skilled user could carry four doses of bo'tous spore. The only documented use of bo'tous spores was in [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]] when the priestess [[Elan]] attempted to assassinate several Jedi by feigning defection to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

